videos.headline: Ramirez hits career high with and-1 jumper in Arkansas' win
videos.description: Arkansas guard Amber Ramirez sinks a deep 2-pointer while drawing a foul to increase her total to 35 on the day in the Razorbacks' win over Alabama.
